Hi AllState,

Thank you for reaching out to Netwrix support.

Please make sure the latest NEA 11.6 is downloaded to the B servers and we can run the upgrade.
There are no prerequisites except that the scheduled scans should be completed/stopped during the upgrade.

It would be also useful to make server snapshots before the meeting to rollback if the upgrade fails.

How many B servers are affected?

Best regards,

Aleksandr Timofeev
